NK059(hi)002:1: // dpal gsang ba snying po'i rgyud kyi bsdus pa'i don
NK059(hi)002:2: ma rig pa'i mun pa thams cad sel ba zhes
NK059(hi)002:3: bya ba bzhugs / bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK059(hi)002:4: dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges
NK059(hi)002:5: pa'i rgyud kyi rgyul po sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba la
NK059(hi)002:7: brjod bya rtogs pa'i yan lag tu mtshan gyi don bshad pa /
NK059(hi)002:8: brjod bya nyid gsal bar ston pa rgyud kyi don dngos bshad pa /
NK059(hi)002:9: yongs su rdzogs pa mjug gi don bshad pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:12: phyag gis mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:13: rgyud don dngos la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:15: de las zhi khro gnyis kyi 'char tshul /
NK059(hi)002:16: rgyud rjes 'jug la gtad pa'i tshul lo //
NK059(hi)002:18: dbyings las ma g.yos par rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor bkod tshul /
NK059(hi)002:19: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par ched du brjod tshul /
NK059(hi)002:20: 'jig rten du sgron ma bkod de chos thams cad gtan la phab tshul lo //
NK059(hi)002:24: rang snang du don bsdu ba'o //
NK059(hi)002:26: longs sku'i ngo bo mdor bstan pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:27: dbye ba rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:35: rgyan dang khri bkod pa phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:37: bzhugs tshul thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:38: yab yum so sor bshad pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:42: rang bzhin ji ltar bzhugs pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:44: nang gi sems dpa' yab dang yum /
NK059(hi)002:45: phyi'i sems dpa' yab dang yum /
NK059(hi)002:46: sgo ba yab dang yum mo //
NK059(hi)002:47: gsum pa rang snang du don bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:48: gang la bkod pa'i ngo bo /
NK059(hi)002:49: ji ltar bkod pa'i tshul lo //
NK059(hi)002:51: gnyis pa chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par ched du brjod tshul la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:52: dgos pa gleng bslang ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:53: ma rtogs pa'i sems can la thugs rje g.yo ba'i tshul lo //
NK059(hi)002:56: gleng ba dngos kyis yab kyi dgongs pa gleng bslang ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:58: gleng ba dngos kyis yum gyi dgongs pa gleng bslang ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:60: gleng ba dngos kyis gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa gleng bslang ba'o //
NK059(hi)002:61: thugs rje g.yo tshul la lnga ste /
NK059(hi)002:62: gzhi ye nas gsang bas sems can gyis ma rtogs pa /
NK059(hi)002:63: ma rig pa'i sems can la thugs rje skye tshul /
NK059(hi)002:64: bdag tu bzung bas 'khor bar 'khrul tshul /
NK059(hi)002:65: 'khrul dus de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos pa'i tshul /
NK059(hi)002:66: ye nas grol ba'i chos ston tshul lo //
NK059(hi)002:68: gsum pa 'jig rten du sgron ma bkod pa la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:82: bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'dul ba /
NK059(hi)002:88: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:89: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin skye med du bstan pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:90: chos kyi rang bzhin brjod med du bstan pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:94: rang bzhin chos nyid du bstan pa /
NK059(hi)002:96: 'khrul rtog rtsa bral du bstan pa /
NK059(hi)002:97: rnam shes ye shes su bstan pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:98: gnyis pa chos kyi rang bzhin brjod med du bstan pa la drug ste /
NK059(hi)002:99: theg pa bzhi'i 'bras bur bstan pa /
NK059(hi)002:100: rang bzhin med pa'i cho 'phrul bstan pa /
NK059(hi)002:101: gang la gang la 'dul du bstan pa /
NK059(hi)002:102: theg pa kun gyi 'phro gzhir bstan pa /
NK059(hi)002:103: mdo rgyud kun gyi spyi 'grel du bstan pa /
NK059(hi)002:104: gnas lugs brjod med du bstan pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:105: gsum pa don bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:106: rang snang du ston pa'i rgyu brjod pa da nga /
NK059(hi)002:107: ji ltar bstan pa dngos so //
NK059(hi)002:109: 'khrul snang sems kyi rang snang du bstan pa /
NK059(hi)002:110: zhing snang ye shes kyi rang snang du bstan pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:113: de las zhi khro gnyis kyi 'char tshul bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:114: zhi ba lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:115: khro bo mngon par 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor bshad pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:117: gzhi dkyil 'khor bskyed cing dbang bskur ba /
NK059(hi)002:118: lam bskyed pa dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa bsgom pa /
NK059(hi)002:119: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:121: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi rang bzhin spyir bstan pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:122: dbang bskur ba'i thabs bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:124: rgyu yi ge sprin gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK059(hi)002:125: de las byung ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK059(hi)002:126: de gsal bar byed pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:128: yi ge sprin gyi dkyil 'khor dgod pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:129: ji ltar bsgrub pa'i rim pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:135: yi ge'i rang bzhin spyir bstan /
NK059(hi)002:136: lha dang sbyar te so sor bshad /
NK059(hi)002:156: tshig gi 'byung khung bstan pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:157: rol pa sprul skur bstan pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:162: gnyis pa lha dang sbyar te bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:167: dbyings rigs lnga yab yum nang sems sgo ba /
NK059(hi)002:170: sgo skyong khro bo dang bcas pa'i yi ge'o //
NK059(hi)002:172: kun tu bzang mo'i yi ge /
NK059(hi)002:173: rigs lnga yab kyi yi ge /
NK059(hi)002:174: rigs lnga yum gyi yi ge'o //
NK059(hi)002:176: dbang po'i sems dbang bzhi thugs kyi sgo ba dang bcas pa'i yi ge dang /
NK059(hi)002:177: yul gyi sems ma bzhi sku yi sgo ba dang bcas pa'i yi ge'o //
NK059(hi)002:180: sems ma sgo ma dang bcas pa'i yi ge'o //
NK059(hi)002:182: ye ge kun tu bzang po'i yi ge dang /
NK059(hi)002:183: sprul sku thub pa drug gi yi ge'o //
NK059(hi)002:187: gsum pa don bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:191: gnyis pa ji ltar bsgrub pa'i rim pa la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:197: yi ge sprin gyi rang bzhin /
NK059(hi)002:198: ji ltar sgrub pa'i thabs so //
NK059(hi)002:200: sems nyid rtsa bar bstan pa /
NK059(hi)002:201: des grub pa mchog gi dngos grub /
NK059(hi)002:204: yi ge sprin gyi rang bzhin la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:207: ji ltar sgrub pa'i thabs la gsum ste bstan /
NK059(hi)002:211: dmigs med spyir bstan pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:212: bye brag tu bshad pas shes rab stong pa nyid /
NK059(hi)002:213: bskyed rdzogs lha yi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK059(hi)002:214: snang srid kun tu bzang po'i phyag rgyar bshad pas thabs snang ba bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK059(hi)002:216: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:217: dbyings ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor spyir bstan pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:218: de'i yan lag sngags dang phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:220: dkyil 'khor spro ba'i rgyu brjod pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:223: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor spyir bstan /
NK059(hi)002:224: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bye brag tu bshad /
NK059(hi)002:225: ye shes chen po'i dkyil 'khor du don bsdu ba'o //
NK059(hi)002:231: brten pa lha yi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK059(hi)002:236: lha yi dkyil 'khor la drug ste /
NK059(hi)002:242: gnyis pa de sgrub pa'i 'bras bu la bzhi ste /
NK059(hi)002:248: gang las byung ba'i dbyings dang /
NK059(hi)002:249: de las byung ba'i phrin las so //
NK059(hi)002:254: sar gnas la snang tshul lo //
NK059(hi)002:255: gsum pa grol tshul la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:256: rgyu lam gyis sgrib pa sbyangs tshul dang /
NK059(hi)002:257: 'bras bu sku dang sa yi thob tshul lo //
NK059(hi)002:262: gsum pa ye shes chen po'i dkyil 'khor du don bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:266: gnyis pa sngags dang phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:281: lha bskyed pa'i sngags la drug ste /
NK059(hi)002:283: thugs kyi sems dpa' yab yum /
NK059(hi)002:285: kun tu bzang po yab yum /
NK059(hi)002:286: thub pa drug gi sngags so //
NK059(hi)002:287: gsum pa phrin las kyi sngags la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:288: spyan drangs zhing bstim pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:289: rig pa'i me tog dor ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:290: dngos grub kyi don du gsol ba gdab pa'i sngags so //
NK059(hi)002:291: gnyis pa dbang bskur ba'i sngags la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:297: byin rlabs kyi snang tshul lo //
NK059(hi)002:298: gsum pa gtan la dbab pa la lnga ste /
NK059(hi)002:305: ngo bo gcig las ma 'das pa /
NK059(hi)002:306: rol pa sna tshogs su 'char ba /
NK059(hi)002:307: gdul bya'i mos pa la snang pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:309: gnyis pa sku phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:313: zhi lam 'bras bu phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK059(hi)002:323: don grub yab yum ste rigs lnga yab yum /
NK059(hi)002:327: kun bzang yab yum gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK059(hi)002:328: gsum pa 'bras bu phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:329: gnas lugs kyi phyag rgya spyir bstan /
NK059(hi)002:330: snang byed kyi phyag rgya bye brag tu bshad /
NK059(hi)002:336: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK059(hi)002:337: gsum pa don mdzad la lnga ste /
NK059(hi)002:340: snang yang gcig las ma g.yos pa /
NK059(hi)002:342: thams cad phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du bstan pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:344: gsum pa de gsal bar byed pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:345: gsungs tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:346: rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:350: gang du dbang bskur ba'i don bsdu ba'o //
NK059(hi)002:352: yum gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:353: yab kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba'o //
NK059(hi)002:369: gnyis pa sbyin sreg la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:372: gnyis pa mchod pa la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:373: ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:374: bde ba chen po'i mchod pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:375: dang po la kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mchod pa dngos dang /
NK059(hi)002:376: ji ltar 'bul ba'i tshul gyis chos can gyi mchod pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:377: chos nyid don dam pa'i mchod pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:378: gnyis pa bde ba chen po'i mchod pa la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:380: shes rab bde ba chen po'i mchod pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:385: rgyal ba mnyes pa dang 'gro ba tshim pas gnas skabs dang /
NK059(hi)002:386: mthar thug gi phan yon no //
NK059(hi)002:387: gsum pa dbang bskur ba la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:393: gnyis pa rdul tshon du dbang bskur ba la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:399: chen po thun mong du bri ba'i cho ga'o //
NK059(hi)002:403: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:407: gsum pa 'bras bu la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:410: gzhan don 'byung ba gsum gyis gzhan don sems las 'byung ba'i 'thad pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:411: ji ltar bsgrub pa'i thabs dang /
NK059(hi)002:417: sku dang ye shes su grub tshul /
NK059(hi)002:418: nang gsal chos skur bzhugs tshul /
NK059(hi)002:419: slar yang sprul sku 'byung tshul lo //
NK059(hi)002:421: gnyis pa dbang bskur ba'i thabs bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:423: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:430: nus dbang bye brag tu bshad /
NK059(hi)002:431: dbang dang mi ldan pa'i skyon bstan pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:433: ting nge 'dzin dang rjes gnang gi nyan pa'i dbang /
NK059(hi)002:434: ting nge 'dzin dang rjes gi gnang gi bsgom pa'i dbang /
NK059(hi)002:435: ting nge 'dzin dang rjes gnang gi phrin las kyi dbang /
NK059(hi)002:436: ting nge 'dzin dang rjes gnang gi 'chad pa'i dbang /
NK059(hi)002:437: ting nge 'dzin dang rjes gnang gi rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang ngo //
NK059(hi)002:438: gsum pa phan yon la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:442: gnyis pa lam bskyed rdzogs bsgoms pa gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:453: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor shes par bya ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:454: lam thabs dang shes rab kyi dkyil 'khor nyams su blang pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:456: cir snang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK059(hi)002:458: gang sgrub thabs kyi yan lag go //
NK059(hi)002:460: snang sems gnyis med kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK059(hi)002:461: sbyor sgrol gnyis med kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK059(hi)002:463: zhi ba dang khro bos 'dzin byed yab kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK059(hi)002:464: zhi ba dang khro bos gzung yul yum gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK059(hi)002:465: rol pa gnyis med kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK059(hi)002:466: sbyor sgrol gnyis med la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:468: thabs chen po gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor /
NK059(hi)002:469: ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK059(hi)002:474: thabs chen po gsang ba la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:477: nyes pas mi gos pa'i rgyu mtshan no //
NK059(hi)002:478: gnyis pa rol pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:480: dkyil 'khor so so'i tshogs mchod do //
NK059(hi)002:482: rang bzhin shes par bya ba /
NK059(hi)002:485: dkyil 'khor so so la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:489: tshom bu lnga pa gsum pa gcig pas zhi ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:491: de sgrub pa la bzhi ste /
NK059(hi)002:492: gang zag gang gis dkyil 'khor gang bsgrub pa'i tshom bu gcig pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:495: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor ji ltar sgrub pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:496: gsum pa gang sgrub thabs kyi yan lag la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:498: mthun pa rkyen gyi yan lag /
NK059(hi)002:499: 'grub pa dus kyi yan lag go //
NK059(hi)002:501: gnyis pa de'i yan lag la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:513: bro gar gyi ting nge 'dzin phan yon dang bcas pa /
NK059(hi)002:517: sbyor sgrol gyi ting nge 'dzin phan yon dang bcas pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:518: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:520: des grub pa gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu /
NK059(hi)002:522: gsum pa don bsdu ba la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:523: kun tu bzang po'i bskyed rdzogs /
NK059(hi)002:525: phra mo'i nyes pas mi gos pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:527: gnyis pa rdzogs rim la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:538: bye brag tu bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:548: shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa /
NK059(hi)002:549: gnyis med 'od gsal gyi rim pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:550: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:551: lta bas thag bcad cing sgom pas nyams su blang bas phyi bskyed pa'i rim pa bstan pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:552: bsgom tshul dang 'bras bu'i sgo nas nang rdzogs rim bstan pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:553: 'od gsal ngos bzung shing de nyid ngo sprad pa'i
NK059(hi)002:554: 'bras bus gsang ba 'od gsal gyi rim pa dang
NK059(hi)002:556: gnyis pa khyad par 'phags tshul la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:559: che ba de las gzhan med pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:560: gsum pa gdams pa'i snod la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:564: gsum pa 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyi rang bzhin la bstod pa la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:578: don gnyis pa khro bo mngon par 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:579: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin /
NK059(hi)002:580: lam ji ltar sgrub pa'i thabs /
NK059(hi)002:581: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes la bstod pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:583: gdul bya las kyi khro bo'i byung tshul dang /
NK059(hi)002:584: 'dul byed ye shes kyi khro bos btul tshul lo //
NK059(hi)002:589: rgyu gang gis bskyed pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:592: dmyal ba dang yi dwags su skyes pas rnam smin gyi 'bras bu sdug bsngal myong ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:593: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu gzhan la 'tshe ba'o //
NK059(hi)002:594: gnyis pa ye shes kyi khro bos btul tshul la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:598: cho 'phrul bzhis dregs pa can zil gyis mnan pa /
NK059(hi)002:599: phrin las drag pos gdug pa can tshar bcad pa /
NK059(hi)002:600: thugs rjes rjes su bzung nas bka' la btags pa'i tshul lo //
NK059(hi)002:602: rgyu ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:604: gnyis pa tshar bcad pa la bzhi ste /
NK059(hi)002:605: gtso bo dang 'khor bkod pas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor bkod pa /
NK059(hi)002:606: dregs pa can rngam sgras rgol ba dang de bsgral bas pho rgyud dngos su bsgral ba /
NK059(hi)002:607: snod dang bcud kyi 'jig rten bsdu ba dang sbyor
NK059(hi)002:608: ba chen po'i rol pas mo rgyud sbyor bas dgyes
NK059(hi)002:609: pa / spro ba'i sbyor ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:611: phra men spros pa dang 'khor rnams rang gi gnas su btang bas 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor sproo ba'o //
NK059(hi)002:612: gsum pa thugs rjes bzung ba la bzhi ste /
NK059(hi)002:613: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag nas /
NK059(hi)002:614: dregs pa can phyung ste khrus byas shing dkyil 'khor
NK059(hi)002:615: gyi zhal bstan pas gnas spar te dkyil 'khor mthong
NK059(hi)002:617: stong khams mnyam du btul ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:618: dkyil 'khor gyi gdan du phul ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:621: dbang mo 'bangs su 'ong bas dregs pa can gyi 'bangs su khas blang ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:622: dbang bskur te bka' bsgo ba'o //
NK059(hi)002:624: gnyis pa lam ji ltar sgrub pa'i thabs la lnga ste /
NK059(hi)002:625: thugs rgyud bskul ba gsang sngags kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK059(hi)002:626: dmigs pa'i rten gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK059(hi)002:639: dbang mo nyer brgyad bskyed pas lha bskyed pa'i sngags dang /
NK059(hi)002:640: ye shes spyan drangs pa'i sngags dang /
NK059(hi)002:641: rig pa'i me tog dor ba'i sngags dang /
NK059(hi)002:642: dngos grub kyi don du gsol ba gdab pa'i sngags dang /
NK059(hi)002:643: phrin las kyi don du gtor ma sbyin pa'i sngags so //
NK059(hi)002:645: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rten gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:652: gdan khri ste rten gzhal yas khang dang /
NK059(hi)002:653: brten pa lha yi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK059(hi)002:655: sku mdog zhal phyag gi rnam pa /
NK059(hi)002:658: phyag mtshan btsun mo'i sbyor tshul dang bcas pas gtso bo'i bzhugs tshul dang /
NK059(hi)002:659: khro mo nyi shu dang dbang mo nyer brgyad kyis 'khor gyi bkod pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:661: gsum pa ji ltar mchod pa'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:666: sgrol ba dang sbyor bas spyir bstan /
NK059(hi)002:667: dam rdzas bdud rtsi dang 'dod yon rgyan gyi mchod pas bye brag tu bshad /
NK059(hi)002:668: thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub 'grub pas phan yon bstan pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:670: bzhi pa dam tshig gi rim pa la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:675: dam tshig chen po'i ngo bo spyir bstan pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:676: bsgrub bsrung gi rnam bzhag bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:678: gsung ba'i dam tshig gzhan las 'phags tshul /
NK059(hi)002:686: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK059(hi)002:687: ngo bo nges tshig dang bcas pa /
NK059(hi)002:688: phan yon nyes dmigs dang bcas pa /
NK059(hi)002:689: rang bzhin dbye ba dang bcas pa /
NK059(hi)002:690: phan yon chen po rgya cher bshad pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:692: rtsa ba dang mi spang zhing dang blang gi yan lag ste ngo bo dang /
NK059(hi)002:693: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi nges tshig go //
NK059(hi)002:694: gnyis pa phan yon nyes dmigs bcas pa la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:698: rtsa ba nyams pa'i nyams grib gzhan la gnod cing rang la 'byung ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:699: yan lag nyams pa'i nyes pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:704: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dbye bas rnam grangs kyi dbye ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:705: chos can dang chos nyid mtha' med pas dam tshig bsam gyis mi khyab par dbye ba'o //
NK059(hi)002:706: bzhi pa phan yon rgya cher bshad pa la lnga ste /
NK059(hi)002:707: 'jig rten pas bstod cing bskur ba /
NK059(hi)002:709: rgyal ba'i spyod yul thob pa /
NK059(hi)002:713: lnga pa phrin las sgrub pa la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:729: mnan pa bro yi las so //
NK059(hi)002:742: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:743: dam can la bka' bsgo ba dang /
NK059(hi)002:744: bro gar gyi phan yon bstan pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:752: gtso bo lnga yi bro gar gyi phan yon /
NK059(hi)002:753: ma mo brgyad kyi phra men brgyad kyi dbang mo nyer brgyad kyi bro gar gyi phan yon no //
NK059(hi)002:754: gsum pa khyad par gzhan smos pa la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:758: gsum pa 'bras bu sku dang ye shes la bstod pa'i tshul la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:759: bstod tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:760: bstod pa rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:762: rigs lnga spyir bstod pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:763: dkyil 'khor gyi dbang phyug la bye brag tu bstod pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:769: phrin las kyi rigs la bstod pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:771: don gsum pa rgyud rjes 'jug la gtad pa'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK059(hi)002:776: lam kun gyi 'bras bur gdams pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:777: gsang ba kun gyi mchog tu gdams pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:779: gdams bya rgyud kyi rang bzhin dang /
NK059(hi)002:780: gang la gdams pa snod kyi che ba'o //
NK059(hi)002:783: lam gzhan de'i rkang stegs su bstan /
NK059(hi)002:784: rnam grangs gzhan gsungs pa'i dgos pa bstan pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:785: gnyis pa gsang ba kun gyi mchog tu gdams pa la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:787: de 'dzin pa'i gang zag lung bstan pa'o //
NK059(hi)002:788: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK059(hi)002:789: rang snang la dgyes pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:790: rang snang gdod ma'i dbyings de nyid du 'pho 'gyur med par bzhugs tshul lo //
NK059(hi)002:791: le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa'o ////
NK059(hi)002:792: spyi don gsum pa yongs su rdzogs pa mjug gi don la gsum te /
NK059(hi)002:793: rgyud gang gi khongs su gtogs pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:796: bdag blo'i yid kyi pad+mo'i khang bzang du //
NK059(hi)002:797: rgyud don sgyu 'phrul nyi zer gsal ba yis //
NK059(hi)002:798: bsdus 'grel 'dab stong ge sar rgyas gyur pa //
NK059(hi)002:799: de yis blo gsal rkang drug dga' bar mdzod //
NK059(hi)002:800: dge ba de yis bdag dang 'gro ba kun //
NK059(hi)002:801: ma lus nyer zhi gdod ma'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK059(hi)002:802: gsang ba'i snying po dam pas legs gzhol te //
NK059(hi)002:803: sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK059(hi)002:804: gang 'dir bdag blo nags ri'i khrod dga' zhing //
NK059(hi)002:805: spros pas skyo la ting 'dzin lhur len na'ang //
NK059(hi)002:806: yang yang bskul phyir snying rje'i rlabs g.yo bas //
NK059(hi)002:807: phyi rabs don 'gyur snyam nas 'di brtsams so //
NK059(hi)002:808: mig ldan rnams kyis gzu bo'i blos sbyar te //
NK059(hi)002:809: ji bzhin don nyid gzigs pas dgongs par 'gyur //
NK059(hi)002:810: lung rigs man ngag rnams bkra'i tshogs mang bas //
NK059(hi)002:811: cung zad mi 'gal legs bshad sprin phung 'khrigs //
NK059(hi)002:812: 'di don rnam bzhi'i legs par bstan pa ni //
NK059(hi)002:813: spyi don yid mkha'i mun pa sel ba dang //
NK059(hi)002:814: bsdus don ma rig mun pa sel ba dang //
NK059(hi)002:815: gzhung don phyogs bcu'i mun pa sel ba dang //
NK059(hi)002:816: lam rim ye shes sgron ma 'bar ba ste //
NK059(hi)002:817: theg mchog sgyu 'phrul tshig don gsal ba yin //
NK059(hi)002:818: rin chen mchog las 'dod dgu sgrub pa bzhin //
NK059(hi)002:819: rgyud don mchog las thar pa bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK059(hi)002:820: blo mig mchog las phun tshogs sgrub pa dang /
NK059(hi)002:821: legs bshad mchog las don gnyis sgrub par mdzod //
NK059(hi)002:822: 'dir ni skye bo dga' ba rnam mang bas //
NK059(hi)002:823: dad ldan don gnyer dga' bas dgyes par mdzod //
NK059(hi)002:824: dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges
NK059(hi)002:825: pa'i bsdus don ma rig pa'i mun pa thams cad
NK059(hi)002:827: theg pa mchog gi rnal 'byor ba rdo rje gzi brjid kyis /
NK059(hi)002:828: gangs ri thod dkar du sbyar ba rdzogs so //
